Macaulay2Editor
Advanced text editor for Macaulay2.

run dependencies:
  libgdbm
  kde4
  sqlite3
  qt

build dependencies:
  tools: 
    cmake

  libraries:
    libgdbm-dev
    kde4-devel
    sqlite3-dev
    qt4-dev
    boost > 1.40.0


HOWTO build.
install all dependencies. 
create folder "build" in source directory 
goto that folder
run "cmake .."


INSTALL:
there is only manual installation for this project.
copy editorui.rc to /home/"username"/.M2E/
enable autocompletion by copying macaulay2.xml to /home/"username"/.kde/share/apps/katepart/syntax/
then just run the editor executable.






